transcription.text: Wasmage is a lightweight, high performance and extensible web assembly run time for cloud
It powers serverless apps, embedded functions, microservices, UDF, smart contracts and IoT
The Wasmage run time provides a well-defined execution sandbox for its contained web assembly
byte code program that run time offers isolation and protection for operating system resources.
